## ✅ what i did  
-clicked start
-opened the terminal
-ran: 'vim bro.s'
-typed: '.intel_syntax noprefix'
        '.global _start'
        '_start:'
        'cmp rdi, 0'
        'jnz loop'
        'mov rax, 0'
        'jmp done'
        'loop:'
        'mov rdx, [rdi]'
        'cmp rdx, 0'
        'jz done'
        'add rax, 1'
        'add rdi, 1'
        'jmp loop'
        'done:'
        'nop'
-ran: 'as -o bro.o bro.s'
-ran: 'ld -o bro bro.o'
-ran: '/challenge/run bro'
-flag popped out

